  `device_id`, `timestamp_sample` (= **last** sample's time).
- VehicleIMU integrates over `IMU_INTEG_RATE` windows (200 Hz â†’ 5 ms), `src/modules/sensors/Integrator.hpp`:
  - trapezoidal (accel): `delta += (val + last_val)*dt*0.5`
  - gyro coning (`IntegratorConing`): `beta += 0.5*((last_alpha + last_delta_alpha/6) Ã— delta_alpha)`;
